reviews.comment:
Absolutely delighted with my experience working with David Piper Vo! From the get-go, David demonstrated a keen interest in understanding my project goals, taking the time to engage in comprehensive discussions about what I aimed to achieve. His dedication was evident when he presented me with an array of recordings featuring diverse background music, allowing me the freedom to choose.

Initially, I had concerns about the loudness of the original recordings, but David expertly reassured me that the end result on the IVR phone system would differ. True to his word, the final outcome sounded flawless, proving his advice spot on. When I encountered hurdles due to limitations imposed by the phone system company, David was an invaluable resource. Through brainstorming sessions, he offered exceptional solutions that ultimately resolved my challenges.

David's communication was consistently prompt and professional throughout our collaboration, which I found immensely commendable. Without hesitation, I wholeheartedly recommend David Piper Vo for anyone seeking top-notch service and a seamless experience. Five stars without a doubt!

This project was for a longer Form documentary. unable to direct David was the problem.  although eventually Through pickups We were able to make it work.This caused Multiple Day delays.
If I could direct him I would be very pleased to use Him again

I must admit that David is a absolute beast! Amazing voice actor and top professional service! 
I can highly recommend David to everyone who are looking to improve their business, with a crispy voice actor!

David is an extremely professional speaker. He did multiple versions of the script and each of being was excellent. I asked for a minor revision because of a mistake I had made (I had broken a splitted sentence on the script and he rightly recited it that way). He was very quick to make the revision. The audio quality is in line with professional standards. I received a raw version and a post-produced version (I chose the latter since it was already in line with the sound I was looking for and was not over produced at all). Overall I am very happy, I will definitely contact him again and push my clients to have him work if they need a native American speaker with his tone of voice!

To say the final product was good would simply be an understatement, it is one thing to deliver a product but to do it in different distinct voices from the start made it a much easier and much faster delivery in the end. I appreciate it and will be ordering again in the future for sure!
Great to work with! Clear directions and great communication!
Hire this guy, he's the REAL DEAL!!

Great experience and cool project ;)
Looking forward to work with you again
